Invocation Name: car chess
des: Car Chess is a worldwide orientation and concentration competition. Your sat nav guides you over a 3x3 chess board and you have to keep an inner eye on where you are. You'll have great fun with friends seeing where their cars end up on the chessboard. Become a CC Grand Master and maybe the World Champion CC Maximus.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
